= Bless =
'''Sphere:''' Special  
'''Level:''' 1  
'''Range:''' 60 yds  
'''Components:''' V, S, M (cross or holy water)  
'''Duration:''' 6 turns  
'''Casting Time:''' 1 turn  
'''Area of Effect:''' 50-ft radius  
'''Saving Throw:''' None  

== Description ==
Confers a +1 bonus to morale and attack rolls to allies in a 50-ft radius. Must be cast before combat begins.

== Special Notes ==
* Treated as a [[Prayer]] in this campaign.
* All casting times and durations are increased by an order of magnitude (round → turn, turn → hour, etc).
* Requires cross and/or holy water.
